Ubuntu:

sudo apt -yqq install gh

===========================================================================


CSE:

cd ~/bin/install
wget https://github.com/cli/cli/releases/download/v2.22.1/gh_2.22.1_linux_amd64.tar.gz
tar xzf gh_2.22.1_linux_amd64.tar.gz
mkdir -p ~/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
cd ~/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
ln -s ../install/gh_2.22.1_linux_amd64/bin/gh

# In a terminal (not under Emacs) run:
git auth login
